# Growth Engine CIN√âMA ‚Äî Project Rules

## Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript strict mode
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4, Shadcn/ui components
- **State**: Zustand (no immer), TanStack Query v5 for server state
- **DB**: PostgreSQL + Prisma v7 with `@prisma/adapter-pg` (NOT standard PrismaClient)
- **Auth**: NextAuth.js v5, `useSession()` on client, `x-user-id` header on server
- **Queue**: BullMQ + Redis (ioredis) ‚Äî jobs go through `renderQueue`, `trainingQueue`, `exportQueue`
- **Storage**: Cloudflare R2 via `src/lib/storage/r2.ts`; local DAS via `src/lib/storage/das.ts`
- **Real-time**: SSE via `/api/jobs/[jobId]/stream` ‚Äî never use WebSockets

## AI Models
Route all generation through `src/lib/models/router.ts` (`routeToModel`).
Model clients live in `src/lib/models/` ‚Äî Kling, Veo3, Luma, Runway, Pika, Minimax, Seedance, HunyuanVideo, SVD, AnimateDiff.
fal.ai utilities: `src/lib/fal/` ‚Äî lighting, enhancement, sync, training, character, proxy.

## Credits
Always call `checkAndDeductCredits()` from `src/lib/credits.ts` BEFORE starting any AI job.
Refund with `refundCredits()` on failure.

## Timeline
Core schema: `src/lib/timeline/schema.ts` ‚Äî `TimelineRecipe`, `Track`, `Clip`.
FFmpeg renderer: `src/lib/timeline/renderer.ts`.
Export pipeline: `src/lib/timeline/export.ts` ‚Üí BullMQ `exportQueue`.

## Vault
Characters: `src/lib/vault/character.ts` ‚Äî face embeddings + LoRA trigger words.
Model lock: `src/lib/vault/model-lock.ts` ‚Äî enforces consistency after 3 renders.

## API Routes
- Protected routes must check `x-user-id` header (set by middleware)
- Always return `{ error: string }` on failure with correct HTTP status
- Cron routes check `Authorization: Bearer ${CRON_SECRET}`
- Worker health routes check `x-health-token: ${WORKER_HEALTH_TOKEN}`

## Code Style
- No `any` unless absolutely necessary ‚Äî use `unknown` + type guards
- Prefer `const` arrow functions for components
- No default exports from lib files ‚Äî named exports only
- All Prisma queries must use the `db` singleton from `src/lib/db.ts`
- No raw SQL ‚Äî use Prisma ORM methods
- Comments only for non-obvious intent ‚Äî never narrate what code does

## Folder Structure
```
src/
  app/           # Next.js App Router pages + API routes
  components/    # React components (ui/, editor/, simple/, ultimate/)
  hooks/         # Custom React hooks
  lib/           # Server-side utilities (db, auth, queue, models, etc.)
  store/         # Zustand stores (editor, vault, jobs)
  workers/       # Standalone BullMQ worker entry points
```
